[i]Constitution[/i] is the general hardiness of a creature. Raising [section:clr-attr]CON[/section] grants a higher [url:values#WT]Wound Treshold[/url] and [url:values#TN]Toughness[/url] and increases the odds of successfully saving against many [url:status]status effects[/url] and spells.
